item.title: CVE-2017-20135|2024-08-05T21:45:25.997Z -- itech -- dating%20script
item.description: A vulnerability classified as critical was found in Itech Dating Script 3.26. Affected by this vulnerability is an unknown functionality of the file /see_more_details.php. The manipulation of the argument id leads to sql injection. The attack can be launched remotely. The exploit has been disclosed to the public and may be used.
